{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_02_02",
  "title": "LizNoir 02 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリの開催が近づく中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――As the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix approached‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.299999959418114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "突然、姫野達幹部に莉央と葵は呼び出しを受けた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rio and Aoi were suddenly summoned by Himeno and the other executives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.299999959418114,
      "endTime": 7.379999923706055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、また遅刻……\nもうしょうがないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ late again…\n…It can’t be helped…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.566666666666666,
      "endTime": 12.825102202097575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央は何気なく街頭の巨大ディスプレイを見上げる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio casually looks up at a giant display on the street.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 16.73333329275145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "地上波のテレビ番組がリアルタイムで流れていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A terrestrial TV program is being broadcast live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.733333333333334,
      "endTime": 19.813333297621277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-mannouncer001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　では次のゲストは\nただ今人気急上昇中のアイドル",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Now‚ our next guest is\n…the idol whose popularity is skyrocketing right now‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1,
      "endTime": 27.74999990463257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-mannouncer002.m4a",
      "text": "な、な、なんとわずかデビュー一年にして\n東京レイーズを満員にしてしまった長瀬麻奈さんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-Amazingly‚ after only one year since her debut‚\n…she sold out Tokyo Rays! Mana Nagase-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.933333333333334,
      "endTime": 36.0333335240682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.099999999999994
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.099999999999994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "な……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 39.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.16666666666666,
      "endTime": 40.33181407848993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、えっと、そんな風に\n言わないで欲しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ um‚ please\ndon’t say it like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.499999999999986,
      "endTime": 46.51346950531005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.70165214538573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "記録はファンのみなさんのおかげですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s all thanks to the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.70165214538573,
      "endTime": 50.14893116950987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.20165214538573
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.20165214538573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "（何よ、それ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(What’s that?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.401652145385725,
      "endTime": 53.88228712081907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "（私と葵がどれだけ努力して）\n（ここまで来たと思っているのよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Do you have any idea how much effort Aoi and I)\n…put into getting this far?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.082287120819075,
      "endTime": 58.323511695861804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.515620454152426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、一体なんなのよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.515620454152426,
      "endTime": 61.487661155064906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.68766115506491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、テレビ相手に熱くなっても\n仕方ないと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ I get that you’re fired up about what’s on TV‚\nbut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.68766115506491,
      "endTime": 65.8129673322042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.02215097149215
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……別に熱くなってないわよ\nそれより、十五分遅刻よ、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m not fired up.\nYou’re fifteen minutes late‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.02215097149215,
      "endTime": 71.37215116222701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "話そらして\nあはは、莉央は分かりやすいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re changing the subject.\nAhaha‚ you’re so easy to read‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5888176381588,
      "endTime": 76.63035950064659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.85548430482548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "うるさいわね\nほら、事務所に行くわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shut up.\nCome on‚ let’s go to the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.85548430482548,
      "endTime": 80.63893090287846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.8554843048255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "なんの用事だろう？\n電話かメールでいいのに、めんどくさいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what it’s about?\nThey could just call or email‚ how annoying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8554843048255,
      "endTime": 84.89348875085516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.08881763815883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方、あと少しでグランプリが始まるのに\nどうしてそんなに緊張感がないのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You‚ the Grand Prix is about to start‚\nwhy aren’t you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.08881763815883,
      "endTime": 91.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、だって僕達はいつでも歌って踊るだけだよ\n舞台がグランプリだろうと関係なくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ because we just sing and dance.\nWhat does it matter if the stage is the Grand Prix or not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.59109599788987,
      "endTime": 98.38023412426317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.55776266455644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "すっごくあるのよ！\nはぁ、まったく貴方は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It matters a lot!\nsigh‚ seriously…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.55776266455644,
      "endTime": 103.312978118658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――いつもの葵とのやりとりに莉央はため息をつく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio sighs at Aoi’s usual response.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5036000669001,
      "endTime": 106.72360009551033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.73693340023343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、おかげでいい感じに肩の力が抜けた気がした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But thanks to that‚ she feels like she’s been able to relax a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.73693340023343,
      "endTime": 109.95693342884366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.13693340023354,
      "endTime": 111.19693339069681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
